entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully assumed Trins Evnar's identity.
entries.journal_entry_description: It's time for you to take the place of Trins Evnar. First, of course, you'll have to eliminate Trins Evnar. You'll also need to eliminate anyone within the Chirq Council who directly knew Trins.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Chirq Council: Assumed Identity - Part Two
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Pendretronics is a legitimate business, and other than its owner, none of the employees are known to be criminals. Do not harm any Pendretronics employees or security guards.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Do Not Kill Any Pendretronics Employees
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Kazic Pendre is the last of Trins' contacts within the Chirq Council. He's also the highest ranking of those contacts. Eliminate Kazic Pendre and find out who Kazic reports to within the Chirq Council.
entries.task03_task_display_string_2: Find the name of Kazic Pendre's Boss
entries.task06_item_name: You activate Kazic Pendre's datapad and download the information within
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Find information on who Kazic Pendre reports to within the Chirq Council. Find Kazic Pendre's datapad.
